nodes.text: Dave Hearn is an actor who portrays FN-0606 in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.

Hearn is a founding member of the British theater company Mischief Theatre. His stage credits include plays such as The Play That Goes Wrong, Peter Pan Goes Wrong, The Comedy About a Bank Robbery and Magic Goes Wrong. He also appears in the BBC comedy series The Goes Wrong Show.
